            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1686046381332-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1686046381332-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce is cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>with the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1686046381329-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1686046381329-x400.jpg",
