          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1686046381329-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cooked rice</strong> with the <strong>harissa chicken &</strong> <strong>roasted veg</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>spiced tomato sauce </strong>and <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
